	   <a name=99932062871809></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99932062871809><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=11&mid=99932062871809>Absolutlely a great money making strategy</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=11&mid=99932062871809#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sat, Sep 1st 1:03 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2> Ok, this is a great strategy, it will make you big bucks when you are low level. I noticed that this board is mainly about high level strategies, but for the newbies that look at this site, here it goes.<br><br> Im not sure whether this works with other classes, but i know it works wit the Wizard. First thing you do is go behind the casters guild in South Qeynos and look around until you spot Daenor Castophor, a "Wizard of the Three." Ask him about Neclo, and he will tell you that Neclo is a friend of his. Then he will give you a note to take to Neclo asking that he teaches you some skills in casting. To find Neclo, also a wizard, go to qeynos hills. Follow the path that leads to West Karana. Stop at the gaurd tower on the side of the road and look around for Neclo Rezzlar. Give him the note, and you will be given a spell. You could use the spell, or you could go to Sneed Galloway's Trading Post in North Qeynos and sell it to him. You will easily make <br>3 pp, 5 gp on this one. And you can repeat this as often as you like. Ta Da, money problems are gone. This small quest really helped me out in the money department. I did it whenever i needed some cash. If you like you can do it over and over and over again to make a lot of money.&nbsp;&nbsp;I guess if you started doing this quest at 9 in the morning, and did it again and again till 8 at night, you could have made almost 500 pp. =)  Almost too good to be true.<br><br> So all you low levels who could really use the money, do this quest as many times as you want to make quick and easy cash. Post if you all have any problems.<br><br> Lvl 8 Wizard- Malahart<br> Lvl 17 Paladin- Malaguile<br> <br> Tholluxe Paells<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
