	   <tr><td colspan=2>Kill bats, skellies, and Orc Pawns. Stay somewhat near the guards and run to them if you need to. If you havent used some training points yet, put a few in the skill area of your weapon of choice. Don't be afraid to smack them a few times with your weapon if need be. Any amount of damage helps. Oh and try to get someone to cast clarity or sow on you. Ask nicely and don't beg, most higher lvl people don't mind buffing low level players.<br><br>Urek<br>37th Ranger<br>Tribunal<br><br>Mytar<br>12th Mage<br>Solseuk Ro<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
